        <title>思念从汽笛开始拉响</title>
        <link>https://realyezhihao.github.io/posts/%E6%80%9D%E5%BF%B5%E4%BB%8E%E6%B1%BD%E7%AC%9B%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8B%89%E5%93%8D/</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 22:55:01 +0800</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://realyezhihao.github.io/posts/%E6%80%9D%E5%BF%B5%E4%BB%8E%E6%B1%BD%E7%AC%9B%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8B%89%E5%93%8D/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;思念从汽笛开始拉响。&lt;br&gt;
一遍一遍，&lt;br&gt;
潮水退去，&lt;br&gt;
漫涨。&lt;br&gt;
好久好久，&lt;br&gt;
孤独被夕阳拉长。&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
